How to Get Your Private Student Debt Discharged via Filing for Bankruptcy

In 2019, is it still possible to get rid of your private student loan debt by filing for bankruptcy? Yes, but it’s so difficult to actually qualify for one that I honestly feel bad in even making it seem like a possibility.

